{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-138-special-isosceles-triangles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Zadatak 138: Posełbeni izosceleski trougao","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotri isosceleni trougao sa dužinom baze, $b = 16$, i nogama, $L = 17$.</p>\n<img alt=\"isosceles triangle with edges named as L - two edges with the same length and base of the triangle as b; and height of the triangle - h from the base of the triangle to the angle between L edges\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/special-isosceles-triangles.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Koristeći Pitagorin teorem, vidljivo je da je visina trougla, $h = \\sqrt{{17}^2 − 8^2} = 15$, koja je jedan manja od dužine osnove.</p>\n<p>Za $b = 272$ i $L = 305$, dobijamo $h = 273$, što je jedan veći od dužine osnove, a ovo je još jedan mali izosceles trougao sa svojstvom da je $h = b \\pm 1$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $\\sum{L}$ za dvanaest malih izoscelenih trouglova koji su $h = b ± 1$ i da su $b$, $L$ pozitivni ceo brojevi.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3f61000cf542c50ff09","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301766,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-138-special-isosceles-triangles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function isoscelesTriangles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nisoscelesTriangles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissio